text.tspan: SS0[0-6] SPI Slave Select lines of SPI bus 0 (the [] is the motor ID)
MOSI[0-1] SPI Master Out Slave In lines
MISO[0-1] SPI Master In Slave Out
SCL/SDA[0-3] I2C clock/data lines for 4 cores
SCL/SDA I2C clock/data lines for up to four myoBrick motor angle ICs
LS_D[0-15] DarkRoom Lighthouse Sensor TS4231 data lines
SS[ESP] SPI Slave Select line for ESP8266
SCK[ESP] SPI clock line for ESP8266
MOSI[ESP] SPI Master Out Slave In line for ESP8266
SS1[7-13] SPI Slave Select lines of SPI bus 1 (the [] is the motor ID)
GP0[0-1] GPIO pins controlled by I2C core 0
GP1[0-1] GPIO pins controlled by I2C core 1
GP2[0-1] GPIO pins controlled by I2C core 2
LS_E[0-15] DarkRoom Lighthouse Sensor TS4231 envelope lines
